OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThunberg pulls out of      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffestival over              
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F'greenwashing'             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Climate activist Greta Thunberg has    
OL,6, pulled out of an appearance at the     
OL,7, Edinburgh International Book Festival  
OL,8, over its links to the fossil fuel      
OL,9, industry.                              
OL,11,FShe had been due to attend an event at 
OL,12,Fthe annual festival on 13 August.      
OL,14,FBut she said she would now not do so   
OL,15,Fbecause the festival receives          
OL,16,Fsponsorship from the Baillie Gifford   
OL,17,Finvestment firm.                       
OL,19,FShe claimed Baillie Gifford "invests   
OL,20,Fheavily in the fossil fuel industry".  
